/* Use cases:
  input: 'fx:dir:col'
  output: { flexDirection: 'column' }
*/
export default Object.assign(Object.create(null), {
  bot: "bottom",
  col: "column",
  dir: "direction",
  fx: "flex",
  lt: "left",
  rt: "right",
  bg: "background",
  txt: "text",
  jf: "justify",
  pd: "padding",
  wd: "width",
  hg: "height"
});
